description: The Colorado native called the matchup between the Rockies and the San Diego Padres at Coors Field on Monday -- the first female to do so in over 20 years.
maintext: The Colorado native called the matchup between the Rockies and the San Diego Padres at Coors Field on Monday -- the first female to do so in over 20 years.
title: Announcer Jenny Cavnar makes MLB history
